---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import AffiliateButton from '../../components/AffiliateButton.astro';

const title = "Elysium Basis vs. Tru Niagen: The Science of Longevity (2026)";
const description = "We analyze the two most prominent NAD+ boosters on the market: Elysium Basis and Tru Niagen. Discover which cellular longevity supplement is best for you.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <article>
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <header class="mb-12 text-center">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-4 block font-semibold">Longevity & Anti-Aging</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          Elysium Basis versus Tru Niagen: The Science of Longevity
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
          <span class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Editorial Review</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Updated May 2026</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Hero Image -->
      <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-12 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4047073/pexels-photo-4047073.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Elysium Basis vs Tru Niagen Longevity Science" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700">
        <p class="lead text-xl italic text-slate-900 mb-8" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          The quest for longevity has shifted from science fiction to cellular science. At the center of this revolution is NAD+, a coenzyme essential for energy metabolism and DNA repair. As we age, our NAD+ levels drop significantly, leading to what scientists call "inflammaging."
        </p>

        <p class="mb-10">
          Today, Wellness Sanctuary analyzes the two most prominent NAD+ boosters on the market: Elysium Basis and Tru Niagen. Both claim to turn back the cellular clock, but their methods differ.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">1. The Cellular Strategy</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-8 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Elysium Basis</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            Developed by world-renowned aging researchers, Basis combines Nicotinamide Riboside (NR) with Pterostilbene (a powerful antioxidant found in blueberries). This dual-action formula aims not only to boost NAD+ but also to activate sirtuins, our "longevity genes."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-12 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Tru Niagen</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            Focuses exclusively on a high-purity, patented form of Nicotinamide Riboside (NR). Its goal is singular: to raise NAD+ levels as efficiently as possible. It is backed by more than 200 published scientific studies and is the choice for those who want a clinical, single-ingredient focus.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">2. Comparison Table</h2>
        
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-slate-900">
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Elysium Basis</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Tru Niagen</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Active Ingredient</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">NR + Pterostilbene</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">NR (Niagen®)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Mechanism</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">NAD+ Boost + Sirtuin Activation</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Direct NAD+ Elevation</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Scientific Backing</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Developed by MIT Scientists</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">20+ Human Clinical Trials</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Purity/Safety</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">NSF Certified for Sport</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">FDA Notified (GRAS)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Best For</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Advanced Anti-Aging Synergy</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Pure Cellular Energy</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">3. Our Editorial Verdict</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-slate-900 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose Elysium Basis if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You are looking for a comprehensive "longevity stack." The addition of Pterostilbene makes it a more holistic choice for those fighting oxidative stress alongside cellular aging.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="elysium-basis" text="Try Elysium Basis" />
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-600 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose Tru Niagen if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You prefer a straightforward, highly researched supplement. It is often recommended for those starting their longevity journey who want to see a documented increase in NAD+ levels without extra variables.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="tru-niagen" text="Try Tru Niagen" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 my-12" />

        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-slate-200">
          <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">🩺</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Longevity Insight</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8">
            NAD+ boosters work best when combined with intermittent fasting or high-intensity interval training (HIIT), both of which naturally stimulate the body’s cellular repair mechanisms.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Are you aging faster than you should?</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-6">
            Take our Biological Age & Longevity Quiz to find the cellular support strategy that fits your current lifestyle and age bracket.
          </p>
          <a href="/quiz" class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-all shadow-md">
            Find My Program
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
